title: P.D. James - Devices and Desires (BBC)
description:
From BBC Radio 4 Extra. Written by P.D. James; Full-cast dramatisation starring Robin Ellis as Adam Dalgliesh; Dramatised by Neville Teller.

A serial killer has claimed four victims and created a climate of fear in the small community of Larksoken on the Norfolk coast. Staying nearby, Adam Dalgliesh is drawn into contact both with the local population and the investigating team.
